-- Juncker Says He’s Confident Ministers to Decide on Greek Rescue on Feb. 20
-- B y   J a m e s   H e r t l i n g
-- 2012-02-15T19:32:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-15/juncker-expects-decisions-on-greece-next-week.html
Luxembourg Prime Minister Jean-
Claude Juncker said he’s confident euro-area finance ministers
will make a decision on a bailout for  Greece  at their next
meeting on Feb. 20. Juncker, chairman of the group, issued a
statement after the ministers held a conference call today on
the Greek package.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  